turn away 转头，回避
She kept trying to kiss me on the mouth, and I kept turning away. 她不断地想要亲吻我，所以我就不停地转头。
Don't you turn away from me. Look at me! 不要回避，看着我！
Lord, help us find the strength to turn away from evil when it tempts us. 天啊，请赐予我们力量逃出恶魔的诱惑吧。
Many people wanted to see the show. 很多人想要看那场演出。
They had to turn away people at the door. 他们不得不在入口处把人们驱走。